org.contentmine.eucl.stml

Class STMLAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • nu.xom.Node
      • nu.xom.Attribute
        • org.contentmine.eucl.stml.STMLAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EuclidConstants, XMLConstants
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleArraySTAttribute, DoubleSTAttribute, IntArraySTAttribute, IntSTAttribute, StringArraySTAttribute, StringSTAttribute

    public class STMLAttribute
extends nu.xom.Attribute
implements XMLConstants
    generic subclassed Attribute for CML elements. often further subclassed into strongly typed attributes in CMLSchema an attributeGroup normally wraps the attribute. Normally the names are the same, but sometimes the attribute group has a different name from the attribute. In some cases two different attributes can have the same name but different attribute groups. The attributeGroup name is only used for collecting the attributes
    Version:
    5.0
    Author:
    Peter Murray-Rust

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(nu.xom.Attribute att)
        compares attributes. As we cannot override Node.equals() which compares identity we have to compare components. order of sorting is: attribute class cmlType name name value null values of any component return -1
        Parameters:
        att - to compare
        Returns:
        0 if all content is identical, -1 if this less than att, 1 if greater value
